---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Pennine Digital - About">
  <section class="pt-44 pb-24 bg-brand-100">
    <div class="relative max-w-lg mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent mb-2">Established 2026</p>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold max-w-sm text-brand-900">
        Building digital homes for <span class="italic">local business.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed max-w-sm text-lg font-thin">
        Pennine Digital is a small web studio based in West Yorkshire, creating websites that feel clear, dependable, and shaped around how
        local businesses actually work. No templates, no shortcuts — just websites built with care.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-background">
    <div class="px-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-heading mb-6 text-brand-900">The person behind the work</h2>

      <p class="text-dark/80">
        I’m Chris — a front‑end developer in Riddlesden, West Yorkshire. I build clear, dependable websites with a calm, considered
        approach.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-5 text-dark/80">
        My background in hospitality taught me how to communicate well, stay organised, and look after people — skills that matter just as
        much in web design.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-5 text-dark/80">
        Pennine Digital is where those things meet: thoughtful development, simple design, and a straightforward way of working with small
        businesses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-28 bg-primary">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-0 max-w-lg md:flex md:justify-between gap-20 text-brand-100 mx-auto">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-highlight">My Approach</p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-brand-200 text-4xl mb-10">
          What matters to me when I <span class="italic">build a website.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-4 text-brand-200/80 max-w-xs font-thin">
          The way a website is built matters just as much as how it looks. These are the principles that guide how I approach every project.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-xs space-y-12 mt-20 md:mt-0">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-brand-200/50 text-sm">01 — Intentionality</p>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl">A clear purpose</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-200/80">
            Everything on a website should earn its place. I focus on clear structure, clean layouts, and decisions that support the message
            rather than distract from it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-brand-200/50 text-sm">02 — Craftsmanship</p>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl">Built with care</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-200/80">
            I build each site by hand, using lightweight, dependable tools. No templates, no bloat — a website that’s put together carefully
            and built to last.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-brand-200/50 text-sm">03 — Accountability</p>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl">Direct communication</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-200/80">
            You work directly with me from start to finish. No layers, no hand‑offs — just honest communication and steady progress from the
            person actually doing the work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background pt-28">
    <div class="px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl text-brand-900">Why I started Pennine Digital</h2>

      <p class="text-dark/80 mt-4">
        I saw a lot of local businesses stuck between expensive agencies and DIY builders that never quite felt right. There was space for
        something more personal — a steady, reliable service that builds websites properly and fits the way small businesses actually work.
      </p>

      <p class="text-dark/80 mt-4">
        That’s what Pennine Digital is for: a small, local studio with a straightforward, honest approach to helping you get online.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="px-6 text-center py-24">
      <h3 class="text-xl text-brand-900/80 mb-10">Ready to chat about your website? I’d love to hear from you.</h3>
      <Button href="/contact" title="Get in touch" variant="main" />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
